**Red Wolves**
__Basics__
Red Wolves always start out with just themselves on their team, however they pretend to be a bloody butcher They win when almost everyone, excluding unaligned players, is dead. In rare circumstances (e.g. through copying or rule changes) the red wolves team may contain more than one player.

__Formalized__
Win Condition: @(Alignment:Red-Wolves), @(Class:Unaligned)
